symmetrization technique

00:34:35.530 --> 00:34:37.649
be used for any other
type of problem?

00:34:40.460 --> 00:34:42.960
YUFEI ZHAO: So the question is,
can the Zykov symmetrization

00:34:42.960 --> 00:34:46.715
technique be used for any
other types of problem?

00:34:46.715 --> 00:34:48.090
I do have something
